This species was originally described by Kozlov and Le from Vietname (
Le 2000
), and Burks et al. 2013 extended its known range to include Thailand, Indonesia, Malaysia and Brunei. These records extend the range to the north to include Guangdong and Zhejiang Provinces. Link to dynamic distribution map: http://hol.osu.edu/map-large.html?id=179750
